title_full:

description: Earlier this year The Caretaker provided closure to a 20 year-long act that has uncannily lurked in the shadows of so many of our listening lives. Jonny Nash and Kyle Martin rekindle their Land Of Light in the quiet new dawn of ‘The World Lies Breathing’ some seven years since their debut with ESP Institute.
